org.trimou.engine

Class MustacheEngineBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trimou.engine.MustacheEngineBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationExtension.ConfigurationExtensionBuilder

    public final class MustacheEngineBuilder
extends Object
implements ConfigurationExtension.ConfigurationExtensionBuilder
    A builder for MustacheEngine. It's not thread-safe. The builder is considered immutable once the build() method is called. Subsequent invocations of any modifying method or build() result in an IllegalStateException.

    Note that most ConfigurationAware components are tied to the specific engine instance and cannot be reused as well.

    Author:
    Martin Kouba
